# Deployment Checklist

See [DEPLOY.md](../../DEPLOY.md) for the full cold-deploy and post-deploy verification checklist. Release train: [ROADMAP.md](../../ROADMAP.md) Status â€” **v2.2.1 code complete** (deploy API first, then Vercel); next gate [PUBLIC_LAUNCH_REVIEW_2026-06-28](../../docs/PUBLIC_LAUNCH_REVIEW_2026-06-28.md) (~Jun 28); [DEVICE_QA_v2.0](../../docs/DEVICE_QA_v2.0.md) manual sign-off; post-deploy verify `hardening_table_rows` > 0 via `scripts/ff-metrics.py`.

## Environment (root `.env`)

All services read a **single repo root** `.env` (see [.env.example](../../.env.example)). Optional sync: `scripts/setup-env.ps1` or `scripts/setup-env.sh`.

Vercel optional: `VITE_TELEGRAM_ANALYTICS_TOKEN`, `VITE_ADSGRAM_REVIVE_ENABLED`, `VITE_ADSGRAM_BLOCK_ID`.

API required for share: `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` (server-side Bot API for `POST /share/prepare`). Optional API: `TELEGRAM_BOT_USERNAME` for challenge links in share copy.

