## 6. Preflight & smoke

From repo root:

```powershell
.\scripts\verify-deploy-config.ps1
.\scripts\smoke-local.ps1
```

Smoke runs: API `pytest`, bot import, mini-app `lint` + `test` + `build` + viewport/layout/coffee QA + SEO verify, deploy preflight.

